reviewText: My daughter loved this combo dvd!  A good collection of Tween romance movies!
My favorite movies all in one pack!
The cinderelle stories are some of my favorite movies and to get em all at one was great. Plus never seen hairspray and loved it. The delivery was fairly fast too

My grand daugher, age 12, enjoyed all 4 of these movies. Some were silly but still funny but then I am a grown-up. The important thing is that she liked them and she will probably watch them over and over again.
